snippet.textDisplay: Coke studio r kache ami prochondo vabe request korbo pls apnara ekta barer jnno ekta indian classical kichu niye ashun. With sitar sarod etc. It is our necessity to get back to our root. R musicians hishebe apnarai to erokom steps neben. Ajker din e classical music er naam i to keo shonena. Tar modde apnara j pahari te sarangi ta dhorlen, khub gorbo holo sotti bolte. Ekhon ektu sitar sarod, shomvob hole santoor er moto prachin classical instruments gulo introduce kore ekbar holeo ekta classical episode niye ashun. We will eagerly remain awaited for that.
